1. Danas je temperatura u Beogradu *visoka*.(Today the temperature in Belgrade is *high*.)
2. Prehlada može da izazove visoku *temperaturu*. (A cold can cause a high *temperature*.)
3. Lekar mi je rekao da merim *temperaturu* svakog dana. (The doctor told me to measure my *temperature* every day.)
4. Čini mi se da je *temperatura* u sobi previsoka. (It seems to me that the *temperature* in the room is too high.)
5. *Temperatura* vode u bazenu je prehladna za plivanje. (The *temperature* of the water in the pool is too cold for swimming.)
6. Ukoliko želite da ispečete kolač, *temperatura* rerne treba da bude 180 stepeni. (If you want to bake a cake, the *temperature* of the oven should be 180 degrees.)
7. Hladnoća u zimskim mesecima može da snizi *temperaturu* tela. (The cold in winter months can lower the *temperature* of the body.)
8. Da bi smanjili *temperaturu* u prostoriji, otvorite prozor ili uključite ventilator. (To reduce the *temperature* in the room, open a window or turn on a fan.)
9. Ukoliko primetite da vam se *temperatura* povećala, odmah se obratite lekaru. (If you notice that your *temperature* has increased, seek medical attention immediately.)
10. Ova medicina se koristi za snižavanje *temperatura*. (This medicine is used to lower *temperatures*.)